creator: Horatio Alger, Jr.
description:
LibriVox recording of Grand'ther Baldwin's Thanksgiving, with Other Ballads and Poems by Horatio Alger, Jr..
Read in English by Diana Schmidt; Albert Christy III; Greg Giordano; Urban Bard; Larry Wilson; Jude; Bruce Kachuk; Andree-Ann Granger; Becca Maggie; SionedV; Will Cooper; Jack Albert
Horatio Alger, better known for his juvenile fiction, also penned some great poetry. His Ballads, including the 8 war poems and his odes, are collected in this volume. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
